  "prompt": "What is the best advice you've received?",
  "response": "One of the best pieces of advice I\u2019ve come across is **\"Focus on progress, not perfection.\"** This reminds us that growth and improvement are ongoing processes, and waiting for everything to be perfect can hold us back. Taking small, consistent steps toward our goals is often far more effective and sustainable than striving for an unattainable ideal. It also encourages self-compassion and resilience when things don\u2019t go as planned. This mindset has helped countless people stay motivated and adaptable in both personal and professional endeavors. What about you\u2014what\u2019s the best advice you\u2019ve received?",
